problems.Title: Easy
problems.Description:
Write a function in python which takes as input an integer n and returns the nth fibonacci number, where the 0th fibbonacci number is 0, and the 1st is 1.

Examples:

Input : 1
Output : 1

Input : 10
Output : 55

problems.Title: Medium
problems.Description:
Given a list, write a Python program to swap first and last element of the list.

Examples:

Input : [12, 35, 9, 56, 24]
Output : [24, 35, 9, 56, 12]

Input : [1, 2, 3]
Output : [3, 2, 1]

problems.Title: Difficult
